{"tid":507151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖南「國保」轟斃公安副局長持槍潛逃 擁「殺40人名單」","createTime":"2017-12-23T02:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-24T15:41:12.000Z","uid":14918,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1b692d928133d1b034afa7acaa6748bcf83794","tid":507151,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"（更新內容）<br />\n湖南婁底市新化縣昨日發生現役警員疑持槍殺人的不尋常案件。當地警員陳建湘在上梅鎮持槍殺人後逃去，省市縣三級公安機關大為緊張，迅速啟動重大案件偵辦機制，正在全力開展圍捕。<br />\n<br />\n海外華文媒體博訊引述消息指，陳建湘槍殺的是一名副局長，另據稱多人被打死。當地網友更指：「他擬好了名單，點名要殺公安局長陳鷹，西河派出所所長，梅苑派出所所長，還有他同事，還有社會上混的大哥，共四十多人」。不過，有關消息仍未經當局證實。<br />\n<br />\n據當局發出的通緝令顯示，涉案警員陳建湘，今年46歲，新化縣上梅鎮人，高約1.71米，身材中等，逃走時上身穿灰色外套，留平頭短髮。案發現場發現1人死亡。公安機關懸賞徵集疑犯行蹤線索，舉報線索協助抓獲嫌疑人的給予5萬元（人民幣‧下同）獎勵，直接抓獲嫌疑人的給予10萬元（12.1萬港元）獎勵，當局對舉報人的資料將予以保密。至於陳建湘行兇動機，當局暫未有透露。<br />\n<br />\n有消息指，陳建湘隸屬國保（國內安全保衞局，負責國內反間諜偵查任務）大隊，有傳他甚至擁有一張列至少有30個名字的殺人名單，而他用以殺人的槍支，則屬於公安局防暴大隊，借槍者現已被扣查，身上有40發子彈。<br />\n<br />\n微博/ 《新京報》"},{"pid":"49544b97a9561555fdb0a4f764dd423de936845f","tid":507151,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171223/large/1513995485_a925.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171223%2Flarge%2F1513995485_a925.jpg&h=9163afc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171223/large/1513995539_9cce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171223%2Flarge%2F1513995539_9cce.jpg&h=a15e7a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171223&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57617003\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171223%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57617003&d=%2F%2B5%2Bqc2hEJKMc6pdDVG3I%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5314cfd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20171223%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57617003&h=0da9156b\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20171223&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57617003</a>"},{"pid":"7d55d236840abc63c2a7fac8d2ef17358b60d541","tid":507151,"uid":49392,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:40:39.000Z","msg":"中國Punisher"},{"pid":"a8ad02509f9873857ad9a96005f72931cec0c813","tid":507151,"uid":53062,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"用天眼好快捉到"},{"pid":"8a0617f4ce066c1331ee5d03e35c89ede03f66f8","tid":507151,"uid":81113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用天眼好快捉到</blockquote><br />\n戴個口罩咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709c198527f89dc1c84d7f5617e448355ed22d64","tid":507151,"uid":232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"支那步步高<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f6bb83711c46bb1d9ca6ad2ddf0b7555a3fc1c","tid":507151,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"30個會唔會少得濟"},{"pid":"866c17cf88c264743a9103209526d1404e359635","tid":507151,"uid":16567,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用天眼好快捉到</blockquote><br />\n戴個口罩咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戴口罩都冇用，大陸買左新技術，跟據身高身形同步行動作去搜尋"},{"pid":"edab525bd062d88bae719b5a141f54350438cda8","tid":507151,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T02:57:07.000Z","msg":"國保 vs 公安"},{"pid":"a3f2f2174db97a8b6f8f06eb5e042f85127927cf","tid":507151,"uid":61115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"單拖殺官員<br />\n勇武真漢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" c